Project Documentation: Automated Network Request Management
ServiceNow Developer Portfolio | K Tanuja
1. Functional Overview
Goal: To modernize IT operations by automating manual network infrastructure requests.
User Story & Experience
•	Self-Service: Users submit requests via the Service Portal.
•	Intelligent Forms: Mandatory fields and data validation prevent incomplete data.
•	Automated Routing: Eliminates manual email chains for approvals.
